Package: grpc
Type: Package
Title: gRPC Library
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Neal Fultz, Google
Maintainer: Neal Fultz <nfultz@gmail.com>
Description: Provides R bindings for the gRPC framework (https://grpc.io/), 
    allowing the creation of gRPC clients and servers within R. Includes 
    functions for reading protocol buffer service definitions and generating 
    client/server interfaces based on Google's Remote Procedure Call system.
